item.title: The Gospel Proclaimed
item.description: I'm currently writing most of this update while on the Gold Coast at the moment. I have had the privilege of joining all the other AFES staff at a con...
item.content:encoded: I'm currently writing most of this update while on the Gold Coast at the moment. I have had the privilege of joining all the other AFES staff at a conference this week. It's been great already to connect with other staff, both new and seasoned, all around Australia (even connecting with some of my old strand leaders from NTE).
item.author: mail@cameronclifford.com (Cameron Clifford)
